{"tid":174480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（鎖國）內房SOHO中國潘石屹，爆外管局落閘","createTime":"2017-03-26T22:47:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-26T23:39:49.000Z","uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0edbf73d25a9bbc2ad9266e2a0de136abfca8b0f","tid":174480,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T22:47:49.000Z","msg":"內房股SOHO中國（410）上周四舉行記者會，當時主席潘石屹被追問點解暫緩變賣資產時，自爆受外滙管制影響而決定停止出售虹口SOHO。&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n潘主席當日似食咗誠實豆沙包，猛話對方係好出名嘅公司，且協議、條款都傾好，想埋位簽合同架啦，點知最後商量完卻決定唔賣，搞到對方「很惱火」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對方嬲嬲豬，潘主席話自己特登寫封信去解釋點解「變卦」，<br />\n<br />\n原來佢<span style=\"color: red;\">本來想將賣樓所得滙到境外分紅，但「現在國家管人民幣、管外滙，這錢不能出去」</span>，<br />\n<br />\n又指揸人民幣現金後無處可投，寧願租金回報率低啲，但揸樓好過揸人民幣咁話，希望對方理解，當時公司總裁閻岩仲搭話「（他們）這就理解了」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但事隔一日即反口，公司官方微博話係「媒體報道與實情不符」"},{"pid":"1fc641294306323d50959817be5f24d27041bd2b","tid":174480,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T23:10:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc791584bf93927c107bdfef76804a3ad90770e1","tid":174480,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T23:18:09.000Z","msg":"誠實豆沙包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01f6c1725afb957d02fa7593ec2414e882f9d35","tid":174480,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T23:30:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>誠實豆沙包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n支那土豪好鐘意忽然爆下大鑊"},{"pid":"ebc709754a9a77d3183d50f14b4165e831123125","tid":174480,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T23:35:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>誠實豆沙包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n支那土豪好鐘意忽然爆下大鑊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢應該俾人照左肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72376db3ffe07d3c9115683a06eb672774173dcc","tid":174480,"uid":65406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T23:39:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>誠實豆沙包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n支那土豪好鐘意忽然爆下大鑊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢應該俾人照左肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n公司黨委立即上報中央掛。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}